    "Table-GPT designs 18 synthesis processes, ranging from table QA to row/column swapping.",
    "For example, the row/column swapping synthesis process swaps rows or columns, and the Output is the swapped table.",
    "In this way, the model can understand the order of rows/columns.",
    "Additionally, Table-GPT implements augmentation strategies at the instruction level, table level, and output level to increase task and data diversity.",
    "For example, the instruction level augmentation uses powerful LLM to paraphrase the canonical human-written instruction into many different variants."
  ],
